creator: FlightInfoApps.com
descriptionHtml:
Let us help to make your visit to Vancouver Airport (YVR) the absolute best it can be.

Looking for flight information?
Trying to find your departure gate?
Looking for somewhere great to eat or drink?
Need to find the rest rooms, go shopping, book a hotel room?
Want to order a taxi.

This app has been designed specifically with you in mind, to make your visit to Vancouver Airport (YVR) a pleasure. Here are the great features that we have built into this app, just for you.

++ DETAILED FLIGHT INFORMATION

We've made great efforts to make our flight arrivals and departures information as clear and easy to use as possible. We've even built in a powerful flight search facility. Want to find a flight by flight number or by city? No problem. You can even search for all flights for a particular terminal or gate. Taxi drivers and baggage handlers have praised us for allowing them to search by terminal and gate.

++ INDOOR TERMINAL MAPS WITH WALKING NAVIGATION

We've harnassed the power of Google Indoor maps and have integrated it right into our app. Imagine you need to get to your gate in a hurry. Simply open up our airport terminal map, move the pin to your gate number and let us give you turn by turn walking directions to your gate. What a time saver.

++ FIND RESTAURANTS, SHOPS, CAR RENTAL AND MORE

We've created a powerful search facility to allow you to find out what is around you in the airport. Our search categories include restaurants, bars, shops, ATM machines, medical facilities, religious facilities and much more.

++ ORDER A TAXI, UBER or HAILO

Find out what Uber cars or Hailo cars are nearby and automatically install or launch the Uber or Hailo apps. We also show you the contact details for the taxi companies that are near your current location.

++ BOOK A HOTEL ROOM

Flight cancelled and need a place to stay? We've integrated hotel room bookings within our app. We show you a list of hotels near the airport and you can book a room from within our app.

++ OTHER AIRPORT INFORMATION

Even more airport information is available, the airport wikipedia information, twitter feed and local weather. Everything you could ever need.

++ INSTALL MORE OF OUR AIRPORT APPS FROM WITHIN THIS APP

You can install any of our other Airport apps directly from within our app. Here are some of the many apps that we have, that may be of particular interest to you - Edmonton, Ottawa, Montreal, Vancouver, Calgary and Toronto

Trying to find your departure gate?
Looking for somewhere great to eat or drink?
Need to find the rest rooms, go shopping, book a hotel room?
Want to order a taxi.

This app has been designed specifically with you in mind, to make your visit to Vancouver Airport (YVR) a pleasure. Here are the great features that we have built into this app, just for you.

++ DETAILED FLIGHT INFORMATION

We've made great efforts to make our flight arrivals and departures information as clear and easy to use as possible. We've even built in a powerful flight search facility. Want to find a flight by flight number or by city? No problem. You can even search for all flights for a particular terminal or gate. Taxi drivers and baggage handlers have praised us for allowing them to search by terminal and gate.

++ INDOOR TERMINAL MAPS WITH WALKING NAVIGATION

We've harnassed the power of Google Indoor maps and have integrated it right into our app. Imagine you need to get to your gate in a hurry. Simply open up our airport terminal map, move the pin to your gate number and let us give you turn by turn walking directions to your gate. What a time saver.

++ FIND RESTAURANTS, SHOPS, CAR RENTAL AND MORE

We've created a powerful search facility to allow you to find out what is around you in the airport. Our search categories include restaurants, bars, shops, ATM machines, medical facilities, religious facilities and much more.

++ ORDER A TAXI, UBER or HAILO

Find out what Uber cars or Hailo cars are nearby and automatically install or launch the Uber or Hailo apps. We also show you the contact details for the taxi companies that are near your current location.

++ BOOK A HOTEL ROOM

Flight cancelled and need a place to stay? We've integrated hotel room bookings within our app. We show you a list of hotels near the airport and you can book a room from within our app.

++ OTHER AIRPORT INFORMATION

Even more airport information is available, the airport wikipedia information, twitter feed and local weather. Everything you could ever need.

++ INSTALL MORE OF OUR AIRPORT APPS FROM WITHIN THIS APP

You can install any of our other Airport apps directly from within our app. Here are some of the many apps that we have, that may be of particular interest to you - Edmonton, Ottawa, Montreal, Vancouver, Calgary and Toronto
